OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fsink southwards into Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fand northern England through this
OL,8,Fevening and overnight, accompanied by
OL,9,Fstrong winds. Frequent showers
OL,10,Ffollowing across Scotland. Staying
OL,11,Flargely dry further south with a few
OL,12,Fmist and fog patches in southern
OL,13,FEngland. Mild.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTuesday:FA wet and windy day in the
OL,16,Fnorth, with heavy rain across parts of
OL,17,Fnorthern England. Blustery showers
OL,18,Fcontinuing for Scotland and Northern
OL,19,FIreland. Generally brighter towards
OL,20,Fsoutheast England.
